window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In the tumultuous span of a week, Kalyn faces the harsh blows of unemployment and eviction. A stroke of fate leads her to a lifeline—a flyer offering a live-in maid position at a billionaire’s mansion. Little does she know, the mysterious employer harbors a secret: <i>a love that he has quietly endured for four long years.</i></p> <p>He falls for her during her darkest hour—her heart getting shattered. Keeping his distance, he silently observes her at the diner where she works.</p> <p>Returning from a business trip he finds she somehow is now employed in his home after being laid off. The very home he envisioned bringing her home to. The boundaries now blur between employer and employee and his unwavering love for her.</p>"; 
